cli_err_skill_not_found_body.en:
Skill '{name}' not found

  Expected path: {path}

How to fix?
  1. Verify skill is installed in ~/.gemini/antigravity/skills/
  2. Reinstall skills:  git pull in antigravity directory
  3. Check permissions:  ls -la {path}

cli_err_skill_not_found_body.es:
Skill '{name}' no encontrado

  Ruta esperada: {path}

¿Cómo resolverlo?
  1. Verifica que el skill está instalado en ~/.gemini/antigravity/skills/
  2. Reinstala skills:  git pull en el directorio de antigravity
  3. Comprueba permisos:  ls -la {path}

cli_err_skill_not_found_body.eu:
'{name}' skill-a ez da aurkitu

  Espero zen bidea: {path}

Nola konpondu?
  1. Skill-a instalatuta dagoela egiaztatu ~/.gemini/antigravity/skills/ bidean
  2. Skills-ak berriz instalatu:  git pull antigravity directorioan
  3. Baimenak egiaztatu:  ls -la {path}

